      <conclusions>
         <blockContainer class="explanatoryNotes">
            <heading>EXPLANATORY NOTE</heading>
            <block name="comment">(This note is not part of the Order)</block>
            <p>This Order specifies the victim surcharge as a relevant penalty for the purposes of section 226I of the Criminal Procedure (Scotland) Act 1995. The Order also specifies the court which imposed the victim surcharge or the court to which the victim surcharge is transferred as relevant courts for the purposes of section 226I in relation to the victim surcharge.</p>
